---
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About.</h2>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          I'm Brandon Simmons, a software developer based in the US. I love the craft of
          building things for the web — from thoughtful user interfaces to backend systems
          that handle real-world complexity.
        </p>
        <p>
          My toolkit spans modern JavaScript (Vue, React, Astro), Python, and a healthy
          appreciation for well-designed APIs. I care about performance, accessibility,
          and the details that make software feel intentional rather than assembled.
        </p>
        <p>
          Outside of work I run a homelab — a small but growing self-hosted
          infrastructure that keeps me close to the ops side of software.
        </p>
        <div class="homelab">
          <p class="homelab-label mono">// homelab stack</p>
          <ul class="homelab-grid">
            <li>
              <span class="hl-name">Proxmox</span>
              <span class="hl-desc muted">bare-metal hypervisor, multiple VMs &amp; LXC containers</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="hl-name">Docker / k8s</span>
              <span class="hl-desc muted">containerised services, experimenting with k3s clusters</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="hl-name">Pi-hole</span>
              <span class="hl-desc muted">network-wide DNS ad-blocking across the LAN</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="hl-name">Self-hosted apps</span>
              <span class="hl-desc muted">password managers, media servers, monitoring dashboards, and more</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="hl-name">Raspberry Pi</span>
              <span class="hl-desc muted">Pi 4 &amp; Pi 5 nodes running lightweight edge workloads</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="hl-name">Home Server</span>
              <span class="hl-desc muted">dedicated machine for storage, monitoring, and experimentation</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="resume-link">
          View Resume →
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="about-photo">
        <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="Brandon Simmons" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60fr 40fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  .homelab {
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .homelab-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--amber);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .homelab-grid {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .homelab-grid li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }
  .hl-name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.825rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .hl-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .homelab-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .resume-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--amber);
    color: var(--amber);
    padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
  }
  .resume-link:hover {
    background: var(--amber);
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .about-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 320px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    outline: 2px solid var(--amber);
    outline-offset: 8px;
    transform: rotate(-1deg);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .about-photo { order: -1; }
    .about-photo img { max-width: 240px; }
  }
</style>
